<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heilman Schildknecht, Wirt des Nürnberger Hofs in Frankfurt am Main und Bürger zu Frankfurt am Main</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Auskunft über den Verbleib der Fürsten zu Frankfurt am Main und das Ergebnis ihrer Besprechungen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="81v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l14">Haylman Schıltknecht vvirte in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l15"><expan>Nüremberg<ex>er</ex></expan> hof cʒü <expan>frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_164_r1l16"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Haylman Als Hans <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l17">ew herauf geſchieden ıſt / vnd ew 
<del rend="strikethrough">gepet </del> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l18">wie ſich das fürbas <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> würd als dann <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ein teil <expan>dan<ex>n</ex>och</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l20">cʒü frankfurt <expan>belib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſind 
<add><ab facs="#facs_164_line_1576586275909_5656">daʒ Jr vns </ab><ab facs="#facs_164_line_1576586280014_5661">das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_164_line_1576586283301_5666">wolt / . </ab></add> / Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / was Jr trefflichs <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> weſte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l22"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht / das ew füglich wer cʒü <expan>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wie es dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l24">geſtallt ſeÿ / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>vvelıche<ex>m</ex></expan> ende ſie dannan <expan>ſcheıd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vverd<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l25">Jr vns das beÿ <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eıgentlıch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l26">Daran beweıſt Jr vns <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> frewntſchaft / die vvir allcʒeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l27"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> vmb ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchuld<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvöllen / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_164" id="81v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Haylman Schiltknecht, wirte in <expan>Nüremberg<ex>er</ex></expan> hof czü
                                <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Haylman, als Hans
                            <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, unser <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von ew herauf geschieden ist und
                        ew <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, wie sich das fürbas
                                <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> würd, als dann
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ein teil <expan>dan<ex>n</ex>och</expan> czü
                        Frankfurt <expan>belib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sind, <add>daz ir uns das
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wolt.</add> Also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, was ir trefflichs
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> weste <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ervare<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht, das ew füglich wer czü
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie es dann gestallt sey
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>weliche<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        ende sie dannan <expan>scheid<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>werd<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz ir uns das bey
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> eigentlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet, daran beweist
                        ir uns <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> frewntschaft, die wir allczeit
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> umb ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schuld<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
